RedirectResult: Represents a redirection to another URL.
StatusCodeResult: Represents an HTTP response with a specific status code.
JsonResult: Represents an HTTP response formatted as JSON.
ContentResult: Represents an HTTP response with content.
CreatedAtRouteResult: Represents an HTTP 201 (Created) response with a location header.
InternalServerErrorResult: Represents an HTTP 500 (Internal Server Error) response.
